(2011,'Austin Pendleton','1940-03-27',6168,NULL,'{}','​From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia.  \n\nAustin Pendleton (born March 27, 1940) is an American film, television, and stage actor, a playwright, and a theatre director and instructor.\n\nDescription above from the Wikipedia article Austin Pendleton, licensed under CC-BY-SA, full list of contributors on Wikipedia.','Warren, Ohio, U.S.','','/5zCfkpsDFAilHv1nMFWiz5lx6ZH.jpg'),
