(4602,'Victoria Cartagena',NULL,118388,NULL,'[\"Victoria Luz Cartagena\"]','From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia.\n\nVictoria Cartagena (height 5\' 6\" (1,68 m)) is a theater and television actress.\n\nVictoria was born in Philadelphia, Pennsylvania. She attended Penn State University, where she earned a degree in education. She was later accepted into the American Musical and Dramatic Academy. Cartagena has starred in numerous theater productions and participated in various plays and workshops for New York\'s Lark Theater. Most recently, Victoria appeared on the WB television series The Bedford Diaries, NBC\'s Kidnapped, and the 2008 season finale of Law and Order: Special Victims Unit.','Philadelphia - Pennsylvania - USA','','/uJ84HU2eEF4skZJ5e4eq9NSJDO1.jpg'),
