(5267,'Kim Raver','1969-03-15',17836,NULL,'[\"Kimberly Jayne Raver\"]','Kimberly Jayne \"Kim\" Raver (born March 15, 1969, height 5\' 8\" (1,73 m) ) is an American actress.\n\nShe is best known for her numerous roles on TV: as Kim Zambrano on Third Watch, Audrey Raines on 24, Nico Reilly on Lipstick Jungle, and, most recently, Teddy Altman on Grey\'s Anatomy.\n\nDescription above from the Wikipedia article Kim Raver, licensed under CC-BY-SA, full list of contributors on Wikipedia.','New York City - New York - USA','','/qxnyB8F1nwVTidvUH2yzh2rsOWS.jpg'),
(5268,'Charlie Murphy','1959-07-12',17840,NULL,'{}','From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia.\n\nCharles Quinton \"Charlie\" Murphy (born July 12, 1959) is an American actor, comedian, writer and widower famous for being a cast member and writer on the Comedy Central sketch-comedy series Chappelle\'s Show. Charlie is also known for his work with his younger brother, actor/comedian Eddie Murphy.\n\nDescription above from the Wikipedia article Charlie Murphy, licensed under CC-BY-SA, full list of contributors on Wikipedia.','Brooklyn, New York, U.S.','','/emMzTjrwhrPr1m8gepw1bvqJb6A.jpg'),
